snippet.title: Industrial I-Spy: Operation Espionage (Dreamcast) - First Mission
snippet.description:
First mission of I-Spy on the Dreamcast. Fun game if you can keep track of different locations in your head. Otherwise it's a complete mess.

www.twitch.tv/lylfox/c/2219133 until Twitch deletes it, but it's exported here on youtube for as long as youtube allows it.

Someday, full run of this thing.
